{
  "text": "Because of hierarchical structure of this data, we corrected regression coefficients and variance estimates for the effects of multilevel clustering, using generalized linear mixed models 40 in Proc GLIMMIX in SAS Version 9.1 (SAS Institute, Cary, NC). We treated physician-level and hospital-level predictors as random effects, to explicitly control for, and evaluate contributions of, specific provider characteristics. [CITATION_1] 42 Physicians who operated in multiple hospitals contributed random effects to each cluster in which they participated.",
